&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315118" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704191911-694x534.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="534" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704191911-694x534.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704191911.jpg 1170w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲电脑采用的 AMD 处理器在 GeekBench 6 单核与多核心测试中，获得 2917、15277 分，属于极高表现&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704192034-607x580.jpg" alt="" width="607" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704192034-607x580.jpg 607w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704192034.jpg 943w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 607px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704193427-694x490.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704193427-694x490.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/20250704193427.jpg 1010w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;▲GeekBench 6 的两个 GPU 测试都超过 20 万分，属于手提电脑中顶级效能表现&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;散热结构与风扇控制&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;重新设计的散热架构，包括大面积气室（Vapor Chamber）、双风扇与超薄 0.05mm 散热鳍片。风道设计经优化，热气主要后排排出，手部不会受热风干扰。风扇模式可在 Synapse 中切换，也支援独立 CPU / GPU TDP 设定。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315151" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/fb_razer0000-1.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;萤幕体验与视觉观感&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Razer 为 Blade 16 配备一块 16 吋 QHD+ 240Hz OLED 面板，支援 0.2ms 反应时间、Calman 认证色彩调校与 G-SYNC，可同时满足游戏与创作需求。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315127" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/fb_razer0032.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315128" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/fb_razer0021.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;键盘、触控板与灯光配置&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;键程提升至 1.5mm，输入手感更饱满。每键支援 RGB 灯效，并加入副功能提示光源，便于操作。新增右侧五枚可编程快捷键，虽可能误触 Enter 键，但习惯后可提升工作流效率。触控板仍保有极大面积，表面滑顺，支援多指手势，但仍偶有误触问题，点击准确性稍受影响。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315135" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/fb_razer0036.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315136" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/fb_razer0041.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315129" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/fb_razer0037.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="580" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315130" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/fb_razer0038.jpg" alt="" width="556" height="580" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315132" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06799-694x359.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="359" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06799-694x359.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06799.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315133" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06800-694x309.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="309" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06800-694x309.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06800.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;▲机身两边的 I/O 提供两组 USB 4、三组 USB 3.2、HDMI 2.1、UHS-II SD 读卡机、3.5mm 音讯孔与 Kensington 锁孔。Wi-Fi 7 / BT 5.4 则为未来连接规格预留。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;总结：旗舰定位无误，升级需审慎考量&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Razer Blade 16（2025）延续系列优良工艺，并在机身厚度与键盘手感上做出实质改善。效能方面，虽 RTX 5090 提升幅度不算突破性，但稳定性与散热表现令人满意，且在薄机设计中已达相当高水准。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;若你是上一代 RTX 4090 用户，未必需要急于升级；但对于追求最新世代 AMD CPU 与 NVIDIA GPU 组合、并重视设计质感与效能的使用者来说，Blade 16 是目前市场上极具竞争力的旗舰选择之一。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1315134" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06802-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06802-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dsc06802-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post &lt;a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/07/04/razer-blade-16-2025-review/notebook/"&gt;Razer Blade 16 (2025) 电竞笔电评测，薄如刀锋、外貌效能兼备&lt;/a&gt; appeared first on &lt;a href="https://unwire.hk"&gt;UNWIRE.HK&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
